Dependency Information

Apache Maven

<dependency>
  <groupId>org.settings4j</groupId>
  <artifactId>settings4j</artifactId>
  <version>2.0.1</version>
</dependency>

Apache Buildr

'org.settings4j:settings4j:jar:2.0.1'

Apache Ant

<dependency org="org.settings4j" name="settings4j" rev="2.0.1">
  <artifact name="settings4j" type="jar" />
</dependency>

Groovy Grape

@Grapes(
@Grab(group='org.settings4j', module='settings4j', version='2.0.1')
)

Grails

compile 'org.settings4j:settings4j:2.0.1'

Leiningen

[org.settings4j/settings4j "2.0.1"]

SBT

libraryDependencies += "org.settings4j" %% "settings4j" % "2.0.1"
